      "blurb": "Female elf gray maiden captain",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> the elf warden of Deathhead — an early, fervent Maiden hunting 'relapse' in her own ranks. Her quarters (E17) display her mother's <strong>+2 invulnerability elven chain</strong> (a Tanglebriar heirloom; convert: +2 resilient mithral chain) and her files: margin-notes in Elven concluding that <strong>Sabina Merrin received far less conditioning than any other Maiden</strong> — leverage she hoards, hoping to take Sabina's place (and cultivate Kordaitra's favor).</p>",
